Cochrane's writing tips: https://www.johnhcochrane.com/s/phd_paper_writing-ajne.pdf

Bellemare's writing guide: http://marcfbellemare.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/BellemareHowToPaperSeptember2020.pdf
  with a presentation linked here: https://marcfbellemare.com/wordpress/12691

Uni Hamburg site with Latex template and more: https://www.wiso.uni-hamburg.de/en/fachbereich-sozoek/professuren/szimayer/teaching/theses/master-theses.html
  and another: https://www.bwl.uni-hamburg.de/en/iwi/studium/abschlussarbeiten.html

The sample thesis .tex file is based on a Uni-Hamburg template, the source of which I cannot find anymore.

The beamer .tex file comes from http://www.LaTeXTemplates.com
  but I added the Metropolis package, because it's the best

